{"lemma":"شَرْحُ","slug":"شَرْحُ","root":"ش.ر.ح","root_slug":"ش-ر-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ر-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شَرْحُ","root":"شرح","pos":"V","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22073","","n22076"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%AD%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to explain","examples":[{"text":"المُعَلِّمُ يَشْرَحُ الدَّرْسَ بِوُضُوحٍ.","english":"The teacher explains the lesson clearly."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut in slices, to slice, to cut up"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bare, to expose"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to comment, to interpret"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to open, to lay open"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to expand"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut in slices, to slice, to cut up"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to dissect, to anatomise"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَرَحَ (šaraḥa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"expounding, presentation, explanation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"commentary","examples":[{"text":"وله في النحو مقدمة حسنة، والمقصود منها أسرار الصنعة وهي عزيزة الوجود، وله كتاب «الكافي في علم العروض والقوافي» وكتاب في إعراب القرآن سماه «الملخص» رأيته في أربع مجلدات، وشروحه لكتاب الحماسة ثلاثة: أكبر وأوسط وأصغر، وله غير ذلك من التواليف","english":"He has a good introduction in grammar, aimed at the secrets of craftsmanship, which are precious. He also has the book “Al-Kafi fi Ilm al-'Arud wa al-Qawafi” (Al-Kafi In The Science of Prosody And Rhyme by Abu Zakariyya at-Tabrizi), and a book in the grammar of the Quran called 'Al-Mulakhass,' which I've seen in four volumes. He has three commentaries for the book 'Al-Hamasah': the major, the middle, and the minor. And he has other compositions as well."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22073","headword_ar":"شَرَحَ","root":"$rH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aroHN","text_ar":"شَرْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uncovered, laid open, displayed, exposed to view, discovered, revealed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disclosed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araHa A^amorahu","text_ar":"شَرَحَ اَمْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He showed, discovered, disclosed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made apparent, his affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araHa masoA^alapF","text_ar":"شَرَحَ مَسْاَلَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He explained a question;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he explained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made manifest, the answer to a question."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araHa AlgaAmiDa","text_ar":"شَرَحَ الغَامِضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He expounded, explained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interpreted, what was obscure, recondite,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abstruse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araHa AlHadiyva","text_ar":"شَرَحَ الحَدِيثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He expounded, explained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interpreted, the tradition; showed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made apparent, its meaning."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araHa","text_ar":"شَرَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. as above, (K,) and so the inf. n., (O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He opened"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA) a thing of any kind, of any substance or material. (TA.) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He defloured"},{"kind":"text","text":"a virgin: (O, K, TA:) or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he compressed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a woman, (A, L,) or a virgin, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lying on her back;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he threw,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"laid, upon her back, and then compressed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"his female slave, or young woman. (O, L.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He widened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dilated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing. (K.) ―         -b6-  Hence, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araHa A@ll~`hu Sadorahu","text_ar":"شَرَحَ ا@للّٰهُ صَدْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, O, Msb, TA,) aor. as above, (TA,) and so the inf. n., (Msb, TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God dilated his bosom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, O, Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liqabuwli Alxayori","text_ar":"لِقَبُولِ الخَيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the acceptance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"favourable acceptance, of what was good"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (O, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liloA_isolaAmi","text_ar":"لِلْاـِسْلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the acceptance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"favourable acceptance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of El-Islám,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the truth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,) as in the Kur [xxxix. 23]. (TA. [Said in the TA to be tropical; but not so in the A, being mentioned in the latter as proper.]) [And hence, an objective complement being app. understood,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN ya$oraHu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يَشْرَحُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY Ald~unoyaA","text_ar":"اـِلَى الدُّنْيَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one manifests desire for the things of the present world:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a one becomes dilated in the bosom at the prospect of the things of the present world, and desirous of acquiring them, with large desire."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, * L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA liY A^araAka ta$oraHu A_ilaY kul~i riybapK","text_ar":"مَا لِى اَرَاكَ تَشْرَحُ اـِلَى كُلِّ رِيبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What aileth me that I see thee manifesting desire for everything occasioning doubt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspicion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil opinion?"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b7-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$r~H","text_ar":"شرّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araHa All~aHoma","text_ar":"شَرَحَ اللَّحْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, O, Msb, TA,) inf. n. as above; (O;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$r~Hhu","text_ar":"شرّحهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, O, Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$oriyHN","text_ar":"تَشْرِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, TA;) the former meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut the flesh-meat lengthwise"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into an oblong slice"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into such slices"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he so cut it much"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into many"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slices"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) or the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut the flesh-meat from the joint or limb:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or both signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut the flesh-meat upon the bone:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aroHu All~aHomi","text_ar":"شَرْحُ اللَّحْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSofiyfuhu","text_ar":"تَصْفِيفُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$oriyHuhu","text_ar":"تَشْرِيحُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aSofiyfu","text_ar":"التَّصْفِيفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a kind of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$oriyH","text_ar":"تَشْرِيح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the cutting"},{"kind":"text","text":"a piece of flesh-meat"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin, so that it is translucent by reason of its thinness, and then throwing it upon the live coals."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b8-  Also, (K,) inf. n. as above, (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He understood"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) speech, or language. (TK.) ―         -b9-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aroHN","text_ar":"شَرْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keeping, preserving,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"guarding."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [And particularly The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"guarding"},{"kind":"text","text":"of seed-produce"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the birds;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAriHN","text_ar":"شَارِحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iraAHapN","text_ar":"شِرَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (see 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xfr","text_ar":"خفر"},{"kind":"text","text":", fourth sentence;) each an inf. n., of which the verb is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araHa","text_ar":"شَرَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["K","S","O","A","TA","L","Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n22076","headword_ar":"شَرْحٌ","root":"$rH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of 1. (S, O, &c.) ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An exposition, explanation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interpretation, in the form of a running commentary, comprising the entire text of the work which it expounds;"},{"kind":"text","text":"distinguished from a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaA$iyap","text_ar":"حَاشِيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a commentary only on particular words and passages: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uruwHN","text_ar":"شُرُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}